INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (215,1,'2014-12-11 12:36:20','2014-12-11 10:36:20','<strong>Our Mission</strong>\r\n\r\nOur mission is to deliver significant business value to our customers worldwide through the effective design, selection and deployment of best-in-class solutions and technologies enabling them to reduce operating costs, improve safety and increase overall profitability, always cognizant of environmental impact.\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Vision</strong>\r\n\r\nOur vision is to be the Trusted Advisor, Partner and Preferred Provider of the Process Industries for Process Systems Simulation Solutions\"\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Commitment</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are dedicated to value creation through improving our customer\'s efficiency and profitability, delivering optimal technology and services capable to radically improve operations, enhance asset utilization and increase reliability and safety. Our commitment is forged with passion around our six below values.\r\n\r\n<strong>Values</strong>\r\n\r\n[av_tab_container position=\'sidebar_tab sidebar_tab_left\' boxed=\'border_tabs\' initial=\'1\']\r\n[av_tab title=\'Excellence &amp; Quality\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'ue800\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\nWe always provide our customers with an excellent product or service, one of quality to be proud of, that meets and exceeds their expectations.\r\n[/av_tab]\r\n[av_tab title=\'People Development\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'ue800\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\nWe recognize and support the desire and ability of individuals to grow and improve. We care to provide both structured as well as on-the-job training, in managerial, technical and sales skills matching training with mentoring, and coaching. We aim at the successful development of people in a career path tailored to each persons abilities and potential.\r\n[/av_tab]\r\n[av_tab title=\'Respect\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'ue800\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\nWe treat everyone with respect at all times. We respect our customers recognizing their needs and objectives. We respect our own colleagues recognizing their strengths, contribution and personal circumstances. We respect our competitors because together we create an environment that pushes us to constantly excel.\r\n[/av_tab]\r\n[av_tab title=\'Innovation\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'ue800\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\nWe nurture and encourage our people\'s desire and ability to be innovative in everything, from products to processes. We foster each person\'s freedom to come forward with technical, business, sales &amp; efficiency ideas and we seek for the opportunities, as well as, the passion and actions to implement those.\r\n[/av_tab]\r\n[av_tab title=\'Accountability\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'ue800\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\nIndividuals, departments, the whole company, we are all and we expect to be held account table for our performance and results. We encourage responsibility on all levels, using initiative, as well as, making sure the result always meets expectations.\r\n[/av_tab]\r\n[av_tab title=\'Profitability\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'ue800\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\nWe strive for sustainable profitability in each business area, project and for our company as a whole as it underpins the financial rewards for our employees and shareholders. Profitability is also the foundation for our freedom to innovate and excel and sustain investment and development for the benefit of our customers.\r\n[/av_tab]\r\n[/av_tab_container]','Vision, Mission & Core Values','','publish','closed','closed','','vision-mission-core-values','','','2014-12-19 16:56:30','2014-12-19 14:56:30','',66,'http://localhost:8000/?page_id=215',3,'page','',0);
