INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (265,1,'2014-12-19 15:39:46','2014-12-19 13:39:46','Plant operators need to train for their work. Similar to the case with pilots and aircrafts, using the actual plant or plant unit as a training tool, is highly costly and dangerous.\r\nProviding a cost effective, safe, and efficient solution, we custom build high-fidelity, real-time simulators to match the dynamic behavior of single or multiple plant units and their associated control and emergency shutdown systems. These are computer and model-enabled systems used to provide plant or unit operators with realistic operation environment to effectively learn how to operate the target process on which a unit runs.\r\n\r\nAn Operator Training System may be used throughout the plant lifecycle to train operating crews, resulting in fewer operating errors and quicker and safer startups and shutdowns, improve plant reliability due to improved response to abnormal situations, optimize throughput and product quality, and provide the basis for evaluation of control strategies.\r\n\r\nBenefits of Operator Training Simulators\r\nDynamic simulation helps process and power generation companies significantly improve overall plant efficiency and bottom line performance and provide the ideal basis for efficient, risk-free operator training and operations improvement. During the past several years, dynamic simulation has been recognized as a key enabling technology in the Process Industries.\r\n\r\n<strong>Operational Skill is a Competitive Advantage</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Faster start-up</li>\r\n	<li>Effective response to Abnormal situations</li>\r\n	<li>Operations team constancy of performance</li>\r\n	<li>Reduced losses and higher levels of production sooner</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Operator Training Simulators is an effective way to develop and sustain operations skills</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Unique safe environment for hands on training</li>\r\n	<li>Reproducible training sessions</li>\r\n	<li>Measurable performance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Added Value from engineering benefits</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Validation of design and configuration (ie DCS check out) before startup</li>\r\n	<li>Operational procedure improvements</li>\r\n	<li>What if analysis</li>\r\n</ul>','Operator Training Simulator','','inherit','open','open','','82-revision-v1','','','2014-12-19 15:39:46','2014-12-19 13:39:46','',82,'http://localhost:8000/2014/12/19/82-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (266,1,'2014-12-19 15:55:25','2014-12-19 13:55:25','<strong>Our Mission</strong>\r\n\r\nOur mission is to deliver significant business value to our customers worldwide through the effective design, selection and deployment of best-in-class solutions and technologies enabling them to reduce operating costs, improve safety and increase overall profitability, always cognizant of environmental impact.\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Vision</strong>\r\n\r\nOur vision is to be the Trusted Advisor, Partner and Preferred Provider of the Process Industries for Process Systems Simulation Solutions\"\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Commitment</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are dedicated to value creation through improving our customer\'s efficiency and profitability, delivering optimal technology and services capable to radically improve operations, enhance asset utilization and increase reliability and safety.\r\n\r\nOur commitment is forged with passion around our six below values.\r\n\r\n<strong>Values</strong>\r\n\r\n[av_tab_container position=\'top_tab\' boxed=\'border_tabs\' initial=\'1\']\r\n[av_tab title=\'Excellence &amp; Quality\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'ue800\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\nWe always provide our customers with an excellent product or service, one of quality to be proud of, that meets and exceeds their expectations.\r\n[/av_tab]\r\n[av_tab title=\'People Development\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'ue800\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\nWe recognize and support the desire and ability of individuals to grow and improve. We care to provide both structured as well as on-the-job training, in managerial, technical and sales skills matching training with mentoring, and coaching. We aim at the successful development of people in a career path tailored to each persons abilities and potential.\r\n[/av_tab]\r\n[av_tab title=\'Respect\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'ue800\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\nWe treat everyone with respect at all times. We respect our customers recogni